# ── Self-dogfood target state ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This repo IS the kit; the canonical SOURCES live in assets/ (helpers, commands,
# builds) + lib/ + tools/. The trees below are runtime state generated when the
# kit operates on a target codebase (including this repo when dogfooding) — ignore
# them so a `bin/ruflo-kit` run never dirties the kit.
.claude/
.claude-flow/
.agentic-qe/
.swarm/
.hive-mind/
node_modules/
.mcp.json
.mcp.json.bak
# package.json + package-lock.json are TRACKED: they are the kit's own vitest
# manifest, which CI (nightly-drift "npm ci" + "npm test") depends on. They are
# kit source, not dogfood runtime state — do not re-ignore them.
agentdb.*
*.rvf
*.rvf.lock
*.rvf.idmap.json
.DS_Store
CLAUDE.md.bak*
CLAUDE.md.backup
CLAUDE copy.md

